In re Resignation of Potts.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Potts (1995), 72 Ohio St.3d 1212.]

(No. 95-660 Submitted April 18, 1995 Decided April 19, 1995.)

The resignation as an attorney of Dominic J. Potts of Steubenville, Ohio, Attorney Registration No., 0029915, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer and Cook, JJ., concur.
